{"tid":1856211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子從武漢紅十字會提1箱3M N95口罩放公務車 司機:給領導配的","createTime":"2020-02-01T13:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T14:50:31.000Z","uid":230104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7faaf2662881536570b48c208d1a56b6224a97e3","tid":1856211,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"2月1日下午2：30左右，武漢市紅十字會借用的武漢市國際博覽中心臨時倉庫外，一名男子從國博中心提出一箱3M口罩，放入一輛車牌為鄂A0260W汽車後備箱，司機稱，領取的物資是給領導配的。<br />\n<br />\n記者多次追問男子及司機所在單位，司機拒絕回答，男子則徑直進入臨時倉庫。<br />\n<br />\n▲鄂A0260W系武漢市政府辦公廳公務用車。網頁截圖經上游新聞記者多方核實，鄂A0260W系武漢市政府辦公廳公務用車。記者撥打了車門上所噴的公務用車監督電話，一直無人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00xwoFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00xwoFq.png&h=9c4d1159&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwDzmr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwDzmr6.jpg&h=8e1dd4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VD0g0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VD0g0r.jpg&h=11216925&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58f5b0200bf7c6661f7867a9782fb18bed571003","tid":1856211,"uid":230104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"香港政府同樣做緊相同既事"},{"pid":"e15c71adfbe7084a467c85720d0f25314e004c8a","tid":1856211,"uid":172668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"香港警察3萬人同家屬都好似話好多"},{"pid":"6afdccc69f7452961751bd9070bed9c0ddb8959b","tid":1856211,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebddbd0e9c4b038eb144819c65737dbc8f22528","tid":1856211,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"關於CSI口罩，記者走去問物流署把撚咩，應該問警務處"},{"pid":"8fde7a158509d880b073e3980ba9d8956